    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(M) In nomine Dei eterni. Anno eius incarnacionis millesimo centesimo XXII,
                        idus octobris, indicione I. Vobis domno <persName key="#Promissio #Castle" ref="#people/3550">Rodulfo</persName> 
                        <orgName key="#Promissio #Castle" ref="#juridical_persons/2075">Sancti Cypriani</orgName> ego <persName key="#marriage #Promissio #Lombard #Castle" ref="#people/3555">India</persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">uxor</rs> <persName key="#marriage #Venditio #Lombard #Castle" ref="#people/3553">Mainfredi</persName> 
                        de <placeName ref="#places/4126">Baone</placeName> quę profiteor lege vivere <rs key="#Lombard">Longobardorum</rs>, ipso viro
                        meo michi consentiente et confirmante, presens presentibus dixi: Promitto et
                        spondeo ego quae supra India una cum meis heredibus vobis domno Rodulfo
                        vestrisque successoribus uti a modo ullo unquam tempore habeamus licentiam
                        nec potestatem per ullum ingenium ullamque occasionern agere vel causare
                        adversus <rs key="#Venditio">vendicionis cartulam</rs> quam Mainfredus vir meus in vos misit de terra
                        de <placeName key="#Castle #Venditio" ref="#places/4127"><rs key="#Castle">castello</rs> de Brenta</placeName>, dicens quod michi 
                        per <rs>morgincap</rs> exinde aliquid
                        pertinere debeat, sed omni tempore taciti et contempti exinde permaneamus.
                        Quod si facere vel agere presumpserimus tunc <rs key="#Penalty">duplam querimoniam vobis
                        restituamus et insuper denariorum Veronensium libras ducentas</rs>; et exinde ego
                        meique heredes taciti permaneamus. Ad hanc enim confinnandam <rs key="#Promissio">promissionis
                            cartulam </rs>accepi ego quę supra India launechilt. Actum in <placeName ref="#places/4442">Terrida</placeName>, feliciter.
                        + Signum manus iam dictę Indię; quae hanc promissionis cartulam fieri
                        rogavit. Rogati sunt <rs key="#Witness"></rs>testes 
                        <persName key="#Witness #Promissio"><name ref="Adam/Gallus">Adam Gallus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Promissio"><name ref="Lemizo/de de Colezade">Lemizo</name></persName> de Colezade, 
                        <persName key="#Witness #Promissio"><name ref="Iohannes/de Pagana">Iohannes</name></persName> de
                        Pagana, <persName key="#Witness #Promissio #childOf"><name ref="Liutulfus/f. Ati/de Gurgo">Litulfus</name></persName> 
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Atto/de Gurgo">Ati</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4443">Gurgo</placeName>. 
                        Ego <persName key="#Notary #Writer #Promissio"><name ref="Heinricus/notarius">Heinricus</name></persName> <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> rogatus
                        <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>. </ab>
                </div>
